nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.35

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.35 is the thirty-fifth issue of the sixth volume of the Star Wars Comic UK published on June 28, 2012. It comes with the free gift of the Bounty Hunter Super Splasher toy and features an episode guide to Deception, Top Tanks, the top 5 mechanised monsters, and Sith Smackdown!, a hypothetical duel between Darth Maul and Savage Opress.
The comic included the comic strip Bacta Raid.
